  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>WELCOME TO THE CAR-COMBAT ARENA!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/671470/extras/39773c95a325f4c3be77ce8238e02778.avif?t=1772271081\" width=604 height=120 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Carsteroids is a fast, skill-based top-down shooter where armed vehicles battle across deadly asteroid arenas.  <br>Master your build, dodge incoming fire, and survive increasingly chaotic encounters.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>GAME MODES:</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Story Mode</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >15 randomly generated stages</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your vehicle between fights</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple endings and final bosses</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/671470/extras/3bd22bf2eab8a06f977880137820911e.avif?t=1772271081\" width=604 height=120 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Arcade Mode</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20-wave survival ladder</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose power-ups after each wave</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face the giant Spider-Tank</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/671470/extras/5e8a852c85910f6e5fa8d2877bc4dc7b.avif?t=1772271081\" width=604 height=120 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Car-ball</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1v1 competitive mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Local multiplayer or CPU</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Score by forcing the ball into your opponent’s field</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/671470/extras/df459abee3ccec649a9e8fe8f31da925.avif?t=1772271081\" width=604 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FEATURES:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 60 FPS responsive combat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Random enemy encounters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple weapons & power-ups</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Couch co-op</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam achievements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gamepad support </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/671470/extras/2473869d51d289e5ccdb45fc92595c6c.avif?t=1772271081\" width=604 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/671470/extras/cf95a5d24a78f0e41339c3b20505c013.poster.avif?t=1772271081\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/671470/extras/cf95a5d24a78f0e41339c3b20505c013.webm?t=1772271081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/671470/extras/cf95a5d24a78f0e41339c3b20505c013.mp4?t=1772271081\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>WELCOME TO THE CAR-COMBAT ARENA!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/671470/extras/39773c95a325f4c3be77ce8238e02778.avif?t=1772271081\" width=604 height=120 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Carsteroids is a fast, skill-based top-down shooter where armed vehicles battle across deadly asteroid arenas.  <br>Master your build, dodge incoming fire, and survive increasingly chaotic encounters.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>GAME MODES:</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Story Mode</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >15 randomly generated stages</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your vehicle between fights</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple endings and final bosses</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/671470/extras/3bd22bf2eab8a06f977880137820911e.avif?t=1772271081\" width=604 height=120 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Arcade Mode</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20-wave survival ladder</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose power-ups after each wave</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face the giant Spider-Tank</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/671470/extras/5e8a852c85910f6e5fa8d2877bc4dc7b.avif?t=1772271081\" width=604 height=120 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Car-ball</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1v1 competitive mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Local multiplayer or CPU</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Score by forcing the ball into your opponent’s field</p></li></